Interface HPGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>

All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
HPListGraph
public interface HPGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>
extends Cloneable<HPGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>>, Generic<NodeType,EdgeType>, java.io.Serializable

This interface represents a HighPerformance Graph which avoids costly object generation by indexing.

The transformation from normal Graph to HPGraph is straight forward, so development with objects and afterwards transformation to higher performance is possible.

There are at least consistency checks as possible, so correct usage is necessary!

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
